description: No prep is required for this super simple, tasty one-tray bake, perfect for a midweek meal.
keywords: Mains,Sausage,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Traybake,Low sugar,Sesame free,High protein,High fibre,Wheat free,Pork,Dinner Made Easy,Peanut free
name: One-Tray Sausage Bake Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500g roast mixed vegetables with garlic and rosemary
400g Italian diced tomatoes no added salt

recipeInstructions.text: Lightly grease a 26 x 20cm 1.5L casserole dish. Add sausages and vegetables and bake for 30 minutes or until sausages are browned.
Toss through tomatoes and turn over sausages. Season to taste. Return to oven and bake for 15-20 minutes or until sausages are well browned and vegetables are tender. Serve with sourdough.
